thread.title: William

author: William
title: William
text: From wheelchairs to Hoyer lifts Med Mart has everything a "medically limited" person could want in order to stay independent in their own home. I just purchased a set of full length arm rests for my Breezy Ultra 4 wheelchair. They were less then $50.00, were here in less then a week, and even came with new screws to attach them to my chair! I rate you guys eleven on a scale of one to ten. Keep up the great work, you've got a customer for life here.
